data.description: Lovely ranch home nestled on 5.12 level, peaceful, wooded acres. There is a 4-car attached garage, 2 in one, 2 in the other. Super nice, covered deck. Open floor plan, with vaulted ceilings and pillars flanking the formal dining room. Wood burning fireplace, hardwood & ceramic floors. Kitchen with island & breakfast bar. Main floor laundry. Office. Wood 6 panel doors. Attic fan. Double hung vinyl tilt-in windows. Full walkout finished basement with another kitchen and fantastic family room and another room used as a guest bedroom with a full finished bathroom. There is also plenty of storage!
